      • getFeatureService

        @NonNull
public java.lang.String getFeatureService()
        Gets the Feature Service that this RosterEntry is bound to on the server. Certain Roster Entries have special characteristics that are managed by server features. Clients may want the ability to distinguish these special roster entries.
        Returns:
        The feature service if found, or empty string if no feature service is found.
        See Also:
        FEATURE_SERVICE_ROLE, FEATURE_SERVICE_ALERTS, FEATURE_SERVICE_PATIENT_CARE
